{"text": "A action packed, team based game. CSGO, it's the face of eSports community. About this game, you get to know about two teams. Terrorists and the Counter-Terrorists. The objectives of both the team varies on the maps. Terrorists on bomb defusal maps have the objective to take hold of the sites and plant the bombs. There's mainly two sites in all bomb defusal map, A and B, each of those sites are either closer to the Counter-Terrorists or the Terrorists. Strategic placing of each team members is the key to the winning of rounds in this mode. Counter-Terrorist's objective on this map is to hold the sites from being taken over by the Terrorists and prevent bomb plants. Each team can eliminate the other team to win the round too. The second map type is the hostage rescue maps. Here terrorists are accountable in holding and protecting the hostages from being escorted by the Counter terrorists. You're mostly packed  in a smaller movement spaces around the hostages while in this mode. Knowning every bits of the map is the key of this mode. Counter-terrorists are given objective on either eliminating the Terrorist side or rescuing the hostages back to the safe zone, which is usually their spawns. Here there's only two scenarios on the winning of Terrorists. Either the time runs out or they eliminate the Counter-Terrorists. Gameplay, you can adapt to different variety of weaponaries ranging from SMGs, Rifles, Heavy weapons and pistols. Each weapon has it's own unique feature and recoil patterns. Some of the easier weapons with easy recoils are the Negev from the heavy group and P90 from the SMGs group. This require minimum skill sets and are the ideal Run and Gun weapons. Ratings. Gameplay. 10/10, if with a squad this game is a perfect fun package. Price. Cheap, totally affoardable and worth the price Graphics. 9/10. A little higher than moderate in the highest settings. Community. 8.5/10, You'd usually get co-operative team-mates and members but there's still a slight chance of getting toxic players. Recommended to all age groups, the ideal FPS game. Note. It is good if you get around the rifles before you jump onto competitive, remembering the recoils and armor penetration on more chance on how you'll win a round.", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198199471263", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1525608000.0}
