{"text": "I pre ordered the ultimate edition on ps4 and again i pre ordered the ultimate edition on steam (No i am not a rich kid). Why? well Game released 24 hours ago and my gameplay time is already 17 hours....anything else you wanna know? :/ oh yah we pc ♥♥♥♥♥♥♥ are lucky to get a game like this TLDR:  Story: 10/10 Graphics: 10/10 Gameplay: 8/10 Over All: 10/10 Now a proper review Optimization: Yah i know everyone is complaining about the graphics or how unoptimized it is, its just rockstar set the bar high. its just way high. you seriously need a mid range to high end pc to play the game properly, by properly i didnt meant \"ULTRA  HIGH\" By that i meant everything looks decent with 50-60 fps. another thing is even if the fps goes low once in a while but still its so buttery smooth you wont notice a thing... Graphics: Graphics is absolute stunning not gonna say much about that it looks same what we so on the trailers. Gameplay: i wouldnt say the gameplay is really good, its just average nothing fancy there. cant complain much about that cause of the next section of the review where the game really shines. and thats why didnt bothered much about the gameplay. Story: I am 29 years old and i am a gamer since i my childhood. i played countless masterpiece but this game is beyond masterpiece. when i finished the game on ps4 at the end of the game i was just holding the controller watching whats happening on my screen and my tears was coming down Automatically down my cheeks....  The way the game starts the way world reacts around your behavior, the way every gang members talk with you i have never seen anything like this ever before. for few people it might seems the story starts kinda slow but thats cause of the story. game wants you to know everyone and slowly introducing every character so that you started to care about them like they really exist. That effects big time in endgame. Rockstar really nailed it big time. Music: another great part of this game. u will get a pure western feel and at the end when u were overwhelmed by emotion there will be some great songs to give you goosebumps multiple times. so yah hands down again !!!! Online: Nothing fancy here tbh. Almost  Every game is fun if you play with your friends. Rockstar will add so many contents in next couple of years that’s for sure (if you are a GTA Online Player you would trust them about that too) But still I wouldn’t recommended the game if only you want to play this game for online. At least not at the current online state of the game. Final Words: We are lucky enough we live in a generation where we get to play a game like THIS. buy the game already guys dont think twice. Rockstar really deserve this", "appid": "1174180", "steamid": "profiles/76561198096876257", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "6", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1575633600.0}
