{"text": "A decent low-budget game but very rough around the edges. If you are willing to look past the few imperfections and the general lack of quality that can be found around almost every corner, from the weird movements, the music that goes on and off on a whim, even the static background noises that can be heard when characters start speaking.. I would wager to say, you will definitely enjoy this one! The story is decent enough and will stick with you for a while. The voices are well performed if you don't mind the poor recording mechanisms. Mini-games are fun and there are even a bunch of extra mini-games once you finish the story. Get it on sale and enjoy the approximately 2 hours long journey!", "appid": "800490", "steamid": "profiles/76561198117501009", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "12", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1572004800.0}
