{"text": "Is a nice zombie shooter, an action game that allows you to have fun time. It can be nicer if you put the multiplayer mode online, not just on the same pc. The graphics are very nice, the pixelated style is awesome! The sound keeps you alive and you can concentrate when you play :) If you have a plan you can forward in a higher wave so you need to have a strategy to stay away from the zombie crouds that can be very agressive and jump on you when you are not looking. The gameplay is easy, a 5 years boy can play this an make a better score than you do. Colors are nice,. All toghether is a nice game that you can buy for just few euros. In the gameplay you have a lot of weapons so it is very funny to play with them and kill the zombies. I like the pixels that jumps in the game and the coins. it can be nicer if some animals are bring into game and attack the main character. It be nicer if the character can have more lifes and respawn after he dies. The map can be larger, it looks to be small. The world detail are nice, but you can add more objects like rocks and obstacles. The bosses are to hard to bead in my oppinion, they have to much health points. If are more zombie types it will be nicer, and more guns types and super powers. The zombies and characters designs are beautiful. They look nice and pixelated XD. Bosses look scary and are to faster for my skill, they beat the ♥♥♥♥ out of me, as an upgrade, you can add steam trading cards into the game with characters of zombies or something like that. The badge can contain 15-20 cards. I will recomment this game to my friends and I hope they will buy this or play together on my pc. I will try to play this game on my live streaming channel and making this i hope i will help the developers to make more games like this one, right here. If i make this, my viewers can see what i play and they will ask me for this game and they will buy it and play because is funny and have a good price. Keep up the good work!", "appi