{"text": "Left 4 Dead meets Red Faction. Dig in with up to 3 other space dwarves (or go solo with your helpful robot pal Bosco) as you mine for treasure while fending off waves of angry insects through randomly generated caverns. Each dwarf class brings its own killer options to the field to deal with hostiles (recently upgraded with a variety of grenades from the Explosive Update) and also mobility options to help the team get through the caverns in one piece. There are a variety of hostile biomes and a handful of mission types to keep you on your toes as well as increases in difficulty.  You use the cash earned from missions/gold mined plus the various resources to upgrade both your gear, unlock new weapons (once you've completed the appropriate level and mission) as well as cosmetics, making each mission feel useful towards progress. All that said, the game can be rather repetitive, so if it doesn't grab you in the first two hours you'll have a good idea if it is for you. Hope to see you in the depths. Rock and Stone!", "appid": "548430", "steamid": "profiles/76561197977469997", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1561809600.0}
