{"text": "**Important note** I am reviewing the game in it's current state as of 27/11/2016 I will update this review later on as the game updates and progresses ** Ever played a game with dinosaurs and thought to yourself \"Man this is cool and all but I would to play as the dinosaur!\" Well then friend this is the game for you. The Isle is a open world survival game where you can choose from a wide variety of dinosaurs both carnivorous and herbivorous to play as. One of the Isle's main features is a \"Progression system\" where you start as the smallest dinosaur and work your way up the food chain towards becoming either an apex predator of the Island or joining a herd with your fellow Herbivores, this progression system however is not forgiving as if you die you are dropped down back to the bottom of the food chain, However there is a checkpoint system in the works that should allow players to save their progress and save them from a long fall back down the food chain. An important note is that the developers are looking for players to help actualy test new features and find any bugs that come with them so that the final game can be more polished and bug free. Make no mistake this is a difficult and unforgiving game but it is not impossible to play provided you have some friends to play with and a way to communicate with each other. The Isle has come a long way since it's debut on steam back in December of 2015 and it still has a long way to go as the game will eventually be adding more important features in like the two human factions, the interactive storyline and much more. Overall I have to give the Isle in it's current state a Positive recommandation as the game is constantly updating and growing and the developers are very vocal and translucent with the community, But if you are someone who does not enjoy difficult games or only has enough time to play casually, take a second thought and read the store page before buying the game just so you know what you are getting yourself into.", "appid": "376210", "steamid": "profiles/76561198018452068", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "11", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1476014400.0}
