{"text": "Sometimes expectations get overriden by reality. You just wanted to explore Africa and enjoy good scenario, boom you are not. This game should be named \"Who killed Captain Alex: The video game\"(not Tiger Mafia included) or \"Rambo: First Blood\" etc. since everything you gotta do is being one man army fighting off bunch of enemies during of civil war, eventually you will forget what was your main task over here in Africa which is killing The Jackal- arm dealer fueling war between two factions by providing weapons for them. But looking from the bright side. In this game you are not hero, you are just a mercenary who wants to earn some cash by messing up with civil war from the both barricades of opposing factions. Malaria is not cool thing but it gives you another side quests which get you some pills supressing that illness, also it forces you to kill more enemies Don't buy this game if: -you want to experience good story -you want to see something new or superior ( this game is like 11 yrs old cmon dude) -you are getting bored doing same stuff all over again -you are used that your character is self regenerating his health slots over time You should totally buy this game if: -you like to see how fire is spreading and taking it's harvest -you don't mind outposts keep getting refilled with enemy forces even if you clean it off -getting chased by 2 random Africans loaded with AK-47's or mounted LMG on the back of their car is your fetish -you want to see how first \"open world wannabe\" Far Cry looked like -jamming weapons could spice your experience little bit than totally ruining it -you value life of your sidekicks coming to help you (yup they are not immortal so appreciate their help) Afterall this game is not designated for every casual player. To enjoy this game properly you have to be open-minded and not to expect some breath taking actions. It's just: You, Africa and infinite numbers of enemies who want you dead.", "appid": "19900", "steamid": "profiles/76561198150262483", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1554465600.0}
