{"text": "It all started with a chicken. A strange, but ultimately normal chicken.  He was a fine lad who was undoubtedly smarter than the average chick. Never got anything below an A in class. The thing was, he was always a little bit odd. Never seemed to talk to anyone. Always speaking to himself. But hey, nobody is perfect. Then came the thirst for blood. Oh dear god. That's when it happened. He went for the horse first. brutally beat the stallion to a pulp, then cut off the limbs and threw him in the dumpster. But this chicken wasn't done yet, as he went on to murder several other civilians in the area. That is what this game is about. Now, the gameplay may come off as insensitive to the poor souls who lost their life on that day, but I truly recommend this game to anyone who wants to give it a try.", "appid": "386940", "steamid": "profiles/76561198150925378", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "6", "votes_funny": "5", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1593086400.0}
