{"text": "Super Killer Hornet: Resurrection è un videogame di genere Bullet Hell - Shoot'em Up sviluppato dalla Flump Studios e pubblicato dalla KISS ltd nel 2014. Il gioco consiste semplicemente nel fare piu' punti,ma una particolarità è quella delle \"operazioni\",dove (durante la partita) si potrà scegliere tra un numero seguito da un simbolo (+,-,x,/) e successivamente un altro numero,dopo di che ci saranno tre risultati e bisognerà indovinare qual'è quello giusto. Ci sono due modalità di gioco: - Arcade. - Time Attack. In modalità Arcade bisognerà semplicemente raggiungere un punteggio sempre piu' alto tramite combo,nemici uccisi e \"operazioni\". In modalità Time Attack l'obiettivo è cercare di sopravvivere prima che il tempo scada,si potranno aggiungere secondi tramite le \"operazioni\". Le difficoltà di gioco sono tre: - Auto-Bomb. - Hard. - Survival. La grafica di gioco è brutta e troppo basilare,la tracklist è fuori tema e anche deludente,la difficoltà di gioco,anche se si selezionerà \"Survival\" rimane molto facile,gli scenari sono tutti uguali e molto ripetitivi,i nemici uno piu' ridicolo degli altri. Assolutamente da evitare. 2.5/10", "appid": "271860", "steamid": "profiles/76561198102275691", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "12", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1423483200.0}
{"text": "Short Summary: The bad: Horribad game - Cannot change shoulders that you aim from, therefore favors aiming and shooting to the right of cover. Cannot aim over left should unless stuck to a wall. Awful controls - shift/double tap W is either roll or sprint, you cannot bind another key and you cannot disable this option, you cannot have split these options up. No secondary weapon (pistol) - you have a primary weapon (AR, smg, sniper shotty) and a melee weapon. No secondary firearm meaning if you get rushed while using a sniper, you have 2 options, go crazy with an axe and hope you dont get shot in the face or use a grenade to try and take them out along with yourself. Extremly laggy, (although ping is not displayed), but is evident by the fact that you can shoot someone, go back into cover, start reloading and then either you or the enemy drop dead mid reload. Shallow game modes, standard run-of-the-mill lobby shooter with no innovative or defining features. Uses third party account to sign up with - does not display EULA, does not display privacy policy, may sell your email to third party companies. Sign up with a dump email account to be safe. The good: Has an uninstall option. Verdict - You'd be better off stepping on Lego, at least that would be more interesting and less painful.", "appid": "315640", "steamid": "profiles/76561198048323387", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1408536000.0}
{"text": "Ok so I dont usually write reviews but this needed to be addressed, I got preorder access to the beta which was up for only a couple of days load times were up to 15mins long just getting to multiplayer and despite numerous performance issues halfway through multiplayer the person I qued up with would run in place and disconnect. Now I know what your thinking why am I saying this? The beta was just a test right? The game has to be fleshed out and in good condition now? Wrong. I love the 40k universe to deathwing (Had to) but the multiplayer is just as broken load times are a tiny bit better still too long for a high end gaming pc running the game at ultra getting over 60fps; the single player is just as bad I get a little bit further everytime but inevitably I freeze and crash i believe its a graphics issue or audio bug due to direct X11 not recognising my card which is really odd. The devs had more than enough time to fix this especially with the extended wait time for launch but they did not address it. I definetley do not recommend buying this unless you want crash simulator. However if the devs resolve this issue I will remove this negative review until then. 10/1000000 would not buy crash simulator 2016 again.", "appid": "298900", "steamid": "profiles/76561198052265340", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1481889600.0}
